ComponentCallbacks, ComponentCallbacks2, KeyEvent.Callback, LayoutInflater.Factory, LayoutInflater.Factory2, View.OnCreateContextMenuListener, Window.Callback
public class PaymentCompletedActivity
extends Activity

Displays the payment completion message.

This activity can only be reached upon successful completion of a payment. For credit card payments, the user can send a receipt. For PayPal transactions, a receipt is automatically sent by PayPal.
